'''''Star Wars Kids'' 18''' is the eighteenth issue of [[Star Wars Kids (1997)|''Star Wars Kids'']] magazine. It was published by [[Scholastic]] and released in [[February]] [[1999]]. Issue 18 included part three of the serial [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] "[[Death Star Pirates]]," written by [[Henry Gilroy]].

''Star Wars Kids'' 18 was available exclusively to subscribers of Scholastic's ''[[Star Wars Missions]]'' young-reader series and [[roleplaying game]], which arrived as monthly continuity packages via direct mail. Each package included a new ''Star Wars Kids'' magazine issue and the latest ''Star Wars Missions'' adventure book. ''Star Wars Kids'' 18 came packaged with the game's eighteenth adventure book, [[Star Wars Missions 18: Rogue Squadron to the Rescue|''Rogue Squadron to the Rescue'']].

